- **Deliverables**: `DeliverableUploadForm.tsx`, `ReviewActionDialog.tsx`, `DeliverableList.tsx`
- **Meetings**: `MeetingCard.tsx`, `AgendaBuilder.tsx`, `ActionItemChecklist.tsx`
- **Forms**: `RichTextEditor.tsx` (TipTap/Quill), `MarkdownViewer.tsx`, `FileUpload.tsx` (Cloudinary integration)
- **Collaboration**: `CommentThread.tsx`, `ActivityFeed.tsx`, `NotificationDropdown.tsx`

